In the Ulam (square) spiral  

 1 is placed at the centre,  
 2 is one step to the right,  
 and the numbers then wind anticlockwise round the origin.

Hence every lattice point (x , y) with k = max{|x|,|y|} lies on the square “ring’’ k whose outer side length is 2k+1 and whose greatest number is  
M(k) = (2k+1)² at the bottom-right corner (k , −k).

For a ring k let  
S(k) = (2k−1)² + 1                      (the first number of that ring).

If the point is on the right side of the ring (x = k , y > −k) its number is

N = S(k) + (y + k − 1).          … (R)

If it is on the bottom side (y = −k , x > −k) its number is

N = S(k) + 7k − 1 + x.         … (B)

--------------------------------------------------
Position of 2026
--------------------------------------------------
45² = 2025 < 2026 < 47² = 2209,  
so 2026 is on ring k = 23.

Because it is the first number of that ring,
2026 = S(23) and lies at (23 , −22) (one square above the bottom-right corner).

--------------------------------------------------
Coordinates and values of the 8 neighbours
--------------------------------------------------
               up-left     up        up-right
               (22,-21)  (23,-21)   (24,-21)

               left      2026       right
             (22,-22)             (24,-22)

             down-left   down      down-right
             (22,-23)  (23,-23)   (24,-23)


1. (24,-22): k = 24, right side → by (R)  
   N = S(24) + ((-22)+24−1) = 2210 + 1 = 2211

2. (22,-22): k = 22, bottom-right corner → M(22)=45² = 2025

3. (23,-21): k = 23, right side → by (R)  
   N = 2026 + ((-21)+23−1) = 2026 + 1 = 2027

4. (23,-23): k = 23, bottom-right corner → M(23)=47² = 2209

5. (24,-21): k = 24, right side → 2210 + 2 = 2212

6. (22,-21): k = 22, right side → S(22) = 1850

7. (24,-23): k = 24, first point of ring 24 → S(24)=2210

8. (22,-23): k = 23, bottom side → by (B)  
   N = 2026 + 7·23 − 1 + 22 = 2026 + 161 − 1 + 22 = 2208

--------------------------------------------------
Sum of the eight neighbours
--------------------------------------------------
2025 + 2027 + 2209 + 2211 + 2212 + 1850 + 2210 + 2208 = 16952

--------------------------------------------------
Answer
--------------------------------------------------
16952
